description:
An heir to http://anidb.net/ch132071 [Jeturk Heavy Machinery], one of the http://anidb.net/ch132088 [group]`s three branches, and a third-year student in the piloting department. Guel has a rough temperament and is quick to anger. As the ace pilot of http://anidb.net/ch125792 [Jeturk House], he has absolute confidence in his own skills.
Source: Official page
name: Guel Jeturk
